<section class="panel">
  <h2>About This Portfolio</h2>
  <p>
    This project is the Node A03 MongoDB integration, built on top of the A02
    view engine refactor. It uses MongoDB Atlas with Mongoose for storing and
    querying projects, categories, and contact submissions.
  </p>
  <p>
    All data is fetched live from the database on each request. A Mini CMS at
    <a href="/admin">/admin</a> provides full CRUD management for projects and
    categories, and lets you view and manage contact form submissions.
  </p>
</section>
